{"tid":2455272,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"巴基斯坦兩男在公路上強暴女子　被判死刑","createTime":"2021-03-21T03:26:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-21T11:53:49.000Z","uid":49648,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ff8f2cae3fd703099d5fc98d1f54badbb6390580","tid":2455272,"uid":49648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:26:58.000Z","msg":"巴基斯坦兩名男子在高速公路上強暴女子，法院判處兩人輪姦、綁架、搶劫和恐怖主義罪成，兩名被告獲判死刑。被告的代表律師表明會上訴。 事發在去年9月，當時受害人駕車外出時，車突然不夠油，滯留在公路上，兩名男子及後闖進車內搶劫和施暴，當時受害人的兩名子女正身處旁邊，引起全國嘩然。一名警員更事後質疑女子為何不選一條更繁忙的路，又或者早些檢查車輛夠不夠油，被批評是把事件歸咎於受害者，結果引發公憤和多次大型示威。 <br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2383920\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2383920&d=naoD8C4w5OVxKX0KwUpsfS3KoYHjImyLH66vjnFGY4M%3D&h=01417e03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2383920</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4834e11af71aa11312cd7234cddb0e0b4a614179","tid":2455272,"uid":177089,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:36:09.000Z","msg":"為何不選一條更繁忙的路，又或者早些檢查車輛夠不夠油<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好有回教國家啲風格"},{"pid":"578b6ccc6b19221b239772b8f91c712c0edf9a80","tid":2455272,"uid":363016,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:36:30.000Z","msg":"恐怖主義有咩關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"971909114eac52e2bbbbf2e40448f59003de1079","tid":2455272,"uid":52215,"like":27,"dislike":5,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"4834e11af71aa11312cd7234cddb0e0b4a614179","tid":2455272,"uid":177089,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-03-21T03:36:09.000Z","msg":"為何不選一條更繁忙的路，又或者早些檢查車輛夠不夠油<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好有回教國家啲風格"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime